<h3 id="setposition-v-vector3-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#setposition-v-vector3-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Matrix4.setPosition" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">setPosition<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( v : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : this</h3>
